      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·南有嘉魚之什·002.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">南山有臺.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>南山有臺，北山有萊。樂只君子，邦家之基。樂只君子，萬壽無期。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the hills of the south is the Tai plant,
On those of the north is the Lai.
To be rejoiced in are ye, noble men,
The foundations of the State.
To be rejoiced in are ye, noble men; --
May your years be myriads and without end!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__xiaoya-nanyoujiayu-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
