      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·南有嘉魚之什·002.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">南山有臺.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>南山有桑，北山有楊。樂只君子，邦家之光。樂只君子，萬壽無疆。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the hills of the south are the mulberry trees,
On those of the north are willows.
To be rejoiced in are ye, noble men,
The light of the State.
To be rejoiced in are ye, noble men; --
May your years be myriads, unlimited!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
