      <prop type="x-translation-ref">南山有臺.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>南山有杞，北山有李。樂只君子，民之父母。樂只君子，德音不已。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the hills of the south are medlars;
On those of the north are plum trees.
To be rejoiced in are ye, noble men,
Parents of the people.
To be rejoiced in are ye, noble men; --
May your virtuous fame have no end!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
