      <prop type="x-translation-ref">南山有臺.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>南山有枸，北山有楰。樂只君子，遐不黃耇。樂只君子，保艾爾後。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>On the hills of the south is the Ju;
On those of the north is the Yu.
To be rejoiced in are ye, gentlemen; --
Will ye not have the grey hair and wrinkled face?
To be rejoiced in are ye, gentlemen; --
May ye preserve and maintain your posterity!</seg>
      </tuv>
